{"word":"H8058 - שָׁמַט - shâmaṭ - shaw-mat' - Discontinue","slug":"H8058","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁמַט</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâmaṭ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-mat'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Discontinue"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DE;&#x05D8; - sha&#x0302;mat&#x0323;</b> - <i>shaw-mat'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>fling</i> down; incipiently to <i>jostle</i>; figuratively to <i>let alone</i>, <i>desist</i>, <i>remit: - </i>discontinue, overthrow, release, let rest, shake, stumble, throw down."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8059\">H8059</a>"}]}